<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:13:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>澳大利亚首次测试先进的SM-6海军防空导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-tests-advanced-sm-6-naval-air-defence-missile-first-time-2024-08-10/</link><description>澳大利亚政府周六表示，首次从海军舰艇上试射了雷神 SM-6 导弹，这是获取防空武器并将其纳入库存的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 06:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-tests-advanced-sm-6-naval-air-defence-missile-first-time-2024-08-10/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜领导人重新视察洪水地区，提出将人们带回首都的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-leader-revisits-flooded-area-offers-plan-bring-people-capital-kcna-2024-08-09/</link><description>据朝鲜官方媒体朝中社报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩本周再次视察了该国与中国边境附近的洪水地区，以解决为近期遭受强降雨和洪水影响的人们提供支持的计划，包括将约 15,400 人带到该国首都，直到新房屋建成。星期六说。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 23:24:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-leader-revisits-flooded-area-offers-plan-bring-people-capital-kcna-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行表示将增加国债交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国央行周五发布的第二季度货币政策执行报告称，中国央行将努力“丰富”货币政策工具箱，并在公开市场操作中逐步增加国债买卖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高管表示调查仍在继续，相信其中国电动汽车措施符合世贸组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</link><description>欧盟执行机构周五表示，欧盟委员会相信其对中国电动汽车国家补贴的调查和针对中国电动汽车补贴的措施符合世界贸易组织的规则，并将继续进行调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者加入重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，菲律宾和越南船只的船员用水炮轰击一艘船只，并模拟搜救，这是两国海岸警卫队在南海与北京对峙的首次联合演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部称欧盟电动汽车初裁违反世贸组织规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟对进口电动汽车（EV）的初步裁决缺乏事实和法律依据，严重违反世界贸易组织（WTO）规则。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>斐济总理将于8月12日至21日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡将于周一至8月21日访问中国，欢迎两国有机会建立战略关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份银行贷款将下降，北京将重点关注政策支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</link><description>路透周五的一项调查显示，尽管央行加大了对经济的政策支持，但受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，中国7月份新增人民币贷款可能较上月大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><description>由于俄罗斯广阔空域飞往欧洲和北美的北方航线较短，中国航空公司享有成本优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份降雨和洪水导致自然灾害损失近一倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</link><description>这是自 2021 年以来 7 月份的最大损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><description>7月份中国消费者价格上涨速度略快于预期，部分原因是天气因素影响了食品供应，而生产者通货紧缩持续存在，使中国的基本消费趋势保持疲软，这是对政策制定者的考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称交易账户不得借用，中国国债下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</link><description>监管机构对中国炙手可热的债券市场涉嫌不当行为展开调查后，官方媒体表示交易账户不得借用或转让，中国国债周五下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>